[metadata]
Name:Terastodon ETB destroys permanents and creates Elephant tokens
Goal:Win
Turns:5
Difficulty:Medium
Description:P0 casts Terastodon (9/9). ETB trigger fires: P0 targets Island (noncreature permanent) for destruction (TargetMax$3, TargetMin$0). Island is destroyed (goes to graveyard). RepeatEach then creates a 3/3 green Elephant token for P1 (the destroyed Island's controller). Regression test for mtg-914: RepeatEach in ETB-trigger sub-ability chain was silently a no-op because extract_effects_from_svar called params_to_effect (no-SVars) instead of params_to_effect_with_svars for RepeatEach, so the DBToken SVar reference could not be resolved.

